  <brief_title>Placebo Effects on Blood Pressure Induced by Expectancy Manipulation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Placebos and Verbal Suggestions on Blood Pressure - Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
